{"tid":1665874,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"用屎做RB係咪無撚敵","createTime":"2019-10-20T17:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T16:27:10.000Z","uid":131980,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7950dc2d0fc10bbd9d343877f3900aacb0f0b646","tid":1665874,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"將屎壓到有2-3米既AREA既無形WALL放係真RB既前2米,佢想跳過去都有難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44c77fb02d22dfb3c1d737196de1a2f4ee7083f","tid":1665874,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:42:46.000Z","msg":"點樣帶去現場，好玩唔玩，玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7ce784eea1f4b62f55a8c16a0ac9362e5aa3cc","tid":1665874,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吸糞車幫到你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1f85a02566d3f269aaee2b8f29da997327c5e0","tid":1665874,"uid":300510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:55:12.000Z","msg":"轉頭硬物並不能令全副武裝的黑警懼怕<br />\n相反嘔心物，如「屎蛋、臭蛋」等&hellip;<br />\n更能令一般人退避和恐懼<br />\n相信會對黑警造成一定的心理壓力<br />\n若然有任何裝備受到染污<br />\n定必馬上想卸下惡臭的隨身裝備<br />\n從而進一步影響其他同袍心態<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（相信你都唔會坐響個周身屎臭嘅人旁邊）</span><br />\n<br />\n重點集中對付<br />\n「狗車」的門柄及窗邊這些必須經常接觸的位置<br />\n令嘔心物更容易散播開其他地方，冷氣入口位置（前方或車頂位置）<br />\n<br />\n「狗屋」的通風系統，如冷氣機、抽氣扇、鮮風入口位置<br />\n停車場、外牆、大門入口及窗亦可，目的令整幢建築物臭氣熏天！<br />\n<br />\n只要大家齊心，毎人自製10至20隻屎蛋<br />\n相信數量一定相當可觀<br />\n非常期待「屎蛋」如雨下的情境招呼黑警和事後中招的黑警的狼狽表現<br />\n<br />\n噁心的臭蛋<br />\n<a href=\"https://elite0905.pixnet.net/blog/post/25928800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felite0905.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F25928800&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=8c73e209\" target=\"_blank\">https://elite0905.pixnet.net/blog/post/25928800</a><br />\n<br />\n如何自製臭雞蛋（須時較長）<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikihow.com/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%AD%E7%82%B8%E5%BC%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikihow.com%2F%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2587%25AD%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BC%25B9&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=63c1dab7\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikihow.com/%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E8%87%AD%E7%82%B8%E5%BC%B9</a><br />\n<br />\n如何自製屎蛋（即成）<br />\n1. 在雞蛋頂端刺穿一個小洞<br />\n2. 用針筒抽出一半蛋液<br />\n3. 用針筒注入糞便混合<br />\n4. 最後用熱溶膠密封小洞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1656372/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1656372/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最後送上一則伊索寓言《風和太陽》作為參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/g9e6yle.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fg9e6yle.html&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=48653b4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/g9e6yle.html</a>"},{"pid":"56b718016425423baf21d52f13b505138f8cbf86","tid":1665874,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"成日見啲人落車搬開啲路障<br />\n淋佢屎就啱㗎啦 咁撚正義呀嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa4d47eb687990f74aa622dd7ba64f1c4251b6d","tid":1665874,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7950dc2d0fc10bbd9d343877f3900aacb0f0b646","tid":1665874,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"將屎壓到有2-3米既AREA既無形WALL放係真RB既前2米,佢想跳過去都有難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:51:46.000Z","msg":"係, <br />\n除非佢用水炮車射爆D屎"},{"pid":"65d7c914ae3580ba225b9c7ba4fda6b34a6aa259","tid":1665874,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T19:53:23.000Z","msg":"警車就唔好用火屬性啦，<br />\n又難着。<br />\n屎屬性就唔同，扔落去有攻擊加成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾人捉到最多都係告你破壞公物姐。"},{"pid":"4925ab9533fa2f1fcbae42a1233d1f35d39996bb","tid":1665874,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f44c77fb02d22dfb3c1d737196de1a2f4ee7083f","tid":1665874,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:42:46.000Z","msg":"點樣帶去現場，好玩唔玩，玩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T20:42:10.000Z","msg":"路邊啲狗糞收集箱幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d799c9ec5a9c64c8633df2637dbfe12ea08113e5","tid":1665874,"uid":143269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T20:49:04.000Z","msg":"有咁多屎就唔駛rb<br />\n全部拋曬落班狗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5dce5c485520f44b5b1fdeceafbacc2203de57","tid":1665874,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T21:06:59.000Z","msg":"召喚屎之鍊金術師"},{"pid":"c60f27198265f06aa6a92741002f155b9ad3ab37","tid":1665874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T21:15:11.000Z","msg":"新職業解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屎法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" c